## Inspiration

ğŸš€ I am inspired by the company [Electricity Maps](https://www.electricitymaps.com/) based in Copenhagen, who allow you to understand the electricity grid through data. They collect data from all around the world and compute the data in an hourly resolution, allowing you to gain granular insights accounting for the variance of the grid.ğŸ’¡
